        public static <E> Iterator<E> iterate(Query<E> query,
                                      int slice)
        Parameters:
        query - BEWARE: The mechanism of this iterator works only, if the query result is stable. This means, the result of the query does not change while iterating. Otherwise, the iterator may miss some results, or return duplicates. Consider using QueryIterators.iterateType(com.exedio.cope.Type, com.exedio.cope.Condition, int) to deal with unstable queries.
